transcripts: Most of my childhood memories we're affected by Eczema. Now dealing with it with my daughter brings back a lot of memories for what it was like for me as a child. Aveeno products have been very important to us to get through this journey. The Aveeno lotions have been great at helping to provide her with relief and it's part of our nightly routine before bed. I know that I'm doing the best thing for her using Aveeno products keeping her Eczema under control and that gives us so much happiness.
